:{{DIcon|Talk}} Have you guys heard about what happened to the Ambrosial Arbor?
::<!--Trigger PerformanceE 502019104: Config/Level/NPCDialogue/P10202/NPCAct/Act502019104.json-->
::'''Wu He:''' Are you talking about the fact that the Ambrosial Arbor no longer sprouts? That's old news to me. Nanjie even advised me to make some immersias about it while it is still a hot topic.
::'''Nanjie:''' Such a great opportunity is hard to come by! You should make immersias about it when the topic is still the talk of the town. In this way, you don't even need to spend much on promotions.
::'''Wu He:''' I don't think it's a good idea. Firstly, we don't know the inside story. Secondly, we won't have the chance to shoot on-site. No one would like to watch such contrived stuff.
::'''Nanjie:''' Don't be so rigid. An immersia about the Ambrosial Arbor doesn't have to include scenes of the real tree. We can film it from the perspectives of the clerks and Cloud Knights from the Realm-Keeping Commission. Just throw in some action scenes and special effects to create tension, and the immersia will do fine.
::'''Wu He:''' If that's the case, the title of the immersia should be ''Legend of Ambrosial Arbor: Prequel'', since the story is only told halfway.
::'''Nanjie:''' Next, we can release one titled ''Agent 001'' about an agent from the Seat of Divine Foresight who runs into some troublemakers on his way to investigate the Ambrosial Arbor...
::'''Nanjie:''' Some funny incidents take place along the way. In the end, everyone realizes the Ambrosial Arbor crisis is nothing but a misunderstanding. It will be a comedy and a crowd-pleaser.
::'''Wu He:''' ...Forget it. You know nothing about immersias...
